Package: tinydenseR
Title: Linking Cell-To-Cell Variation to Sample-to-Sample Variation
Version: 0.0.3.0001
Authors@R: 
    person("Pedro", "Milanez-Almeida", , "pedro.milanez@novartis.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8285-957X"))
Description: tinydenseR is a landmark-based platform for single cell data analysis that identifies differential cell states and features, including subtle within-cluster state changes. Modeling samples as replicates, tinydenseR enhances analytic efficiency and reproducibility while preserving the richness of single cell data.
